moji\" />"},{"pid":"4c096c1ab0a202bf2ee55d1708eaeda3ceffa675","tid":1531974,"uid":104086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:42:01.000Z","msg":"租屋要比兩上一按<br />\n你儲左未  <br />\n襯而家酒店平住酒店仲好係真 又唔洗執房做家務 <br />\n但真心唔知會平到幾時 一定要加緊腳步儲錢<br />\n<br />\n講真 一個人住湯房都開心好多 <br />\n好多套房4000左右 <br />\n工廈葵涌知邊都好多企理5000有廁"},{"pid":"8b75a018ae221ea373fc3a5524d2e2dcd3be4b4f","tid":1531974,"uid":265962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:42:03.000Z","msg":"有無朋友合租？唔厭遠既話 屯門 元朗d村屋租都叫平"},{"pid":"136a2f97298ff52c8b1c947e119eff3bcd272703","tid":1531974,"uid":77547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:43:00.000Z","msg":"馬灣太陽營，ok的"},{"pid":"66be5c7e1890a0864a09783b33f78cbadb51b0db","tid":1531974,"uid":305414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b0c548ac102517c1e6f941c29a10a371cc2e89d6","tid":1531974,"uid":133784,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9404d9bc27a5a5b24782bbee1da74b5861480296","tid":1531974,"uid":19217,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:38:01.000Z","msg":"算啦 忍下儲下錢先啦"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:38:50.000Z","msg":"如果佢地趕我／侮辱我<br />\n就得番呢條路"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:43:06.000Z","msg":"忍"},{"pid":"aab3196fe08d6039952ffe50191b688c952e70df","tid":1531974,"uid":2446,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:43:22.000Z","msg":"Logic fail<br />\n穩定後都唔應該比家用<br />\n因為佢地有祖國同黨做後盾"},{"pid":"61fe21b5cf85a64648b30ed91b94895ef698c230","tid":1531974,"uid":195574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:44:02.000Z","msg":"除非你十級想走，唔係既話就到真係趕先走。<br />\n事實始終岩岩起步，唔穩陣呀<br />\n你地有無傾話政治野？有好多手足既雙親都開始動搖，唔好咁灰住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fa8e8a5d24842b965cd2909f3e1975b17741093","tid":1531974,"uid":133784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:44:12.000Z","msg":"我都知租要準備一舊錢<br />\n所以開頭應該係搵酒店先<br />\n其他再慢慢儲